{"tid":826583,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"全港市民都望你比樹壓死呀 臭閪娥","createTime":"2018-09-18T10:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T11:09:27.000Z","uid":79789,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ff4fd75c96ea6b69dabdb0bc7421be6f543b752f","tid":826583,"uid":79789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"全日係街望住個天黎行<br />\n<br />\n啲樹枝條條fing <br />\n<br />\n都唔撚知幾時會跌落黎<br />\n真係萬分感謝清道夫們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母臭閪娥<br />\n因住比天收 全港都望你返到官邸門口比樹壓死<br />\n<br />\n咁樣樣夠膽叫人返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔叫啲樹互讓下 睇準啲跌？<br />\n<br />\n究竟香港啲樹仲有幾多係安全 好多都歪哂"},{"pid":"e3207db085e75eafcfe6848c63b0b2eaecc4d13b","tid":826583,"uid":79789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:35:46.000Z","msg":"有無專家入黎講解下 啲樹撐到幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b02e510ff27528b2728eb743540b3ad1525bb10","tid":826583,"uid":25378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"香港人真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8764c2e4393bb6fcb06d23a0864bafdb3acce2fe","tid":826583,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:47:19.000Z","msg":"正字 蛾<br />\n<br />\n淋病蚏蛾"},{"pid":"d841be2c0d1476d956235db81c23bfec410a26b1","tid":826583,"uid":79789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b02e510ff27528b2728eb743540b3ad1525bb10","tid":826583,"uid":25378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"香港人真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:02:49.000Z","msg":"唉 人心惶惶<br />\n好多人都掛住手機同呀頭解釋遲到<br />\n好少人睇頭頂有無危險<br />\n平時驚踩狗屎<br />\n依加驚中頭獎"},{"pid":"ccf61d2ab161177781df842edcf79aae0222cf5b","tid":826583,"uid":2